<%- include("template/header") %>
<link rel="stylesheet" href="css/guides.css">
<link rel="stylesheet" href="css/background.css">


    <div class="container-fluid">
        <span class="mx-auto">Pomodoro Method</span>
    </div>

<div class="guide-section">
    <h2>Summary</h2>
    <p>
        The Pomodoro Method is a time-management technique that enhances focus and productivity by breaking study sessions into intervals,
        typically 25-45 minutes long, separated by short breaks. This method helps maintain high levels of concentration and prevents burnout.
    </p>
</div>

<div id="guideCarousel" class="carousel slide" data-bs-ride="carousel">
    <div class="carousel-inner">
        <div class="carousel-item active">
            <div class="guide-section">
                <h2>Step 1</h2>
                <p>Use our Timer in <a href="/study/session">Study Session</a>: Choose a task to work on and set a timer for 25 minutes. Focus solely on this task without distractions.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="carousel-item">
            <div class="guide-section">
                <h2>Step 2</h2>
                <p>Work: Work on the task until the timer rings. If you get distracted, write down the distraction and get back to the task immediately.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="carousel-item">
            <div class="guide-section">
                <h2>Step 3</h2>
                <p>Short Break: Take a 5-minute break after the timer rings. Use this time to relax and clear your mind.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="carousel-item">
            <div class="guide-section">
                <h2>Step 4</h2>
                <p>Repeat: After four Pomodoro sessions, take a longer break of 15-30 minutes to recharge.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="carousel-indicators">
        <button type="button" data-bs-target="#guideCarousel" data-bs-slide-to="0" class="active" aria-current="true" aria-label="Slide 1"></button>
        <button type="button" data-bs-target="#guideCarousel" data-bs-slide-to="1" aria-label="Slide 2"></button>
        <button type="button" data-bs-target="#guideCarousel" data-bs-slide-to="2" aria-label="Slide 3"></button>
        <button type="button" data-bs-target="#guideCarousel" data-bs-slide-to="3" aria-label="Slide 4"></button>
    </div>
    <div class="d-flex justify-content-between mt-3">
        <button class="btn btn-primary" type="button" data-bs-target="#guideCarousel" data-bs-slide="prev">Prev</button>
        <button class="btn btn-primary" type="button" data-bs-target="#guideCarousel" data-bs-slide="next">Next</button>
    </div>
</div>

